mixin calc-sm-v-2(addClass)
    form(class=`${addClass} flex-shrink-0 bg-white rounded-3xl py-6 px-5`)
        div(class="text-lg font-semibold") Выберите сумму и срок займа
        div(class="text-sm mt-2 ") Одобряем 91% при регистрации через Госуслуги
        div
            div(class="flex justify-between items-center mt-4")
                div(class="text-sm") Сумма займа
                div(class="text-5C text-xs") до 30 000 руб
            div(class='mt-4')
                div(class="sum flex")
                    div(class="sum__minus w-8 h-8 border border-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-base leading-none flex-shrink-0") -
                    div(class='px-2 flex-grow')
                        label(class="border border-blue h-8 rounded-[2rem] flex flex-grow items-center justify-center overflow-hidden text-base font-semibold px-4")
                            input(type="number" name="sum" value="30000" class="sum__count font-semibold text-base text-right max-w-[4rem] mr-1")
                            div руб
                    div(class="sum__plus w-8 h-8 border border-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-base leading-none flex-shrink-0") +
            div(class='mt-6')
                div(class="period flex")
                    div(class="period__minus w-8 h-8 border border-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-base leading-none flex-shrink-0") -
                    div(class='px-2 flex-grow')
                        label(class="border border-blue h-8 rounded-[2rem] flex flex-grow items-center justify-center overflow-hidden text-base font-semibold px-4")
                            input(type="number" name="period" value="30" class="period__count font-semibold text-base text-right max-w-[1.5rem] mr-1")
                            div дней
                    div(class="period__plus w-8 h-8 border border-blue rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-semibold text-base leading-none flex-shrink-0") +
        div(class="border-t border-BD mt-4")
            div(class="mt-4")
                div(class="flex items-center justify-between mt-4")
                    div(class="text-sm") Вы возвращаете
                    div(class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 h-6 text-white bg-blue rounded-[2rem]")
                        span(class="text-base font-semibold") 16 000 руб
                div(class="flex items-center justify-between mt-4")
                    div(class="text-sm") До (включительно)
                    div(class="flex items-center justify-center px-4 h-6 text-white bg-blue rounded-[2rem]")
                        span(class="text-base font-semibold") 11.12.2021
        div(class="mt-8")
            button(type='submit' class="gradient-btn rounded-[6.8rem] flex items-center justify-center w-full h-12 text-white text-sm font-semibold hover:opacity-80") Получить деньги
        div(class="text-center mt-6")
            a(href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center text-xl hover:opacity-80")
                div(class='text-sm mr-4') Регистрация через
                img(src=require('./images/elements/gos.png') class="w-20" alt="")